Author: sugacube_68
Text: Thank you, I really appreciate this. I’m trying my best to distract myself with funny videos since distractions help, but I just needed some encouragement so thanks for that. 💜💙

Author: torileighhh
Text: Take your mind somewhere else. Anywhere at all. Watch a movie, take a shower, do some self care. Skincare routine, do a deep conditioning treatment on your hair. Take this time to love yourself instead of destroying. The bread will be long gone tomorrow. ❤️
